{"title":"Hexo+GitHub搭建博客(macOS)","uid":"592e9f37694957087a386212a17b585a","slug":"Hexo+GitHub的副本9","date":"2020-08-15T10:49:36.000Z","updated":"2021-08-29T08:01:50.286Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo+GitHub的副本9.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"安装-GIT\"><a href=\"#安装-GIT\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 GIT\"></a>安装 GIT</h2><h3 id=\"检验是否安装git\"><a href=\"#检验是否安装git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"检验是否安装git\"></a>检验是否安装git</h3><p>使用如下命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> --version<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>然后回车，显示如下git版本号，表示已经安装过git。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>git version 2.30.1 (Apple Git-130)</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"安装git\"><a href=\"#安装git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装git\"></a>安装git</h3><ol>\n<li>使用如下命令，先检查是否安装homebrew。<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>如果终端显示如下输入，则已安装<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Homebrew 3.2.9</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>未安装，则使用如下命令安装<code>homebrew</code><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">/usr/bin/ruby -e <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>安装Git，在Terminal中输入命令：<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">git</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"安装Node-js\"><a href=\"#安装Node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Node.js\"></a>安装Node.js</h2><p>安装之前先判断是否需要安装nvm（node版本管理工具）为了以后方便建议安装，若不想安装nvm，第二步忽略</p>\n<h3 id=\"直接安装Node-js\"><a href=\"#直接安装Node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"直接安装Node.js\"></a>直接安装Node.js</h3><p>终端输入</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> node<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>验证是否安装成功</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">node -v\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>npm 是node第三方插件管理工具，安装node时，npm也自动安装</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"先安装nvm，再通过nvm安装node\"><a href=\"#先安装nvm，再通过nvm安装node\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"先安装nvm，再通过nvm安装node\"></a>先安装nvm，再通过nvm安装node</h3><ol>\n<li>检查是否安装node.js<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">node -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n已安装node，则用以下命令检查安装地址后删除<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">which node<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n删除后验证一下<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">node -v\nnpm -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li>若还未安装node.js，可直接安装nvm<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">curl -o- https:&#x2F;&#x2F;raw.githubusercontent.com&#x2F;creationix&#x2F;nvm&#x2F;v0.33.2&#x2F;install.sh<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n用命令看看是否安装成功<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">nvm<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n若提示如下，则可能缺少.bash_profile 文件配置<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>-bash: nvm: command not found<br>打开文件，将下面代码复制进去</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">export NVM_DIR&#x3D;&quot;$HOME&#x2F;.nvm&quot;\n[ -s &quot;$NVM_DIR&#x2F;nvm.sh&quot; ] &amp;&amp; . &quot;$NVM_DIR&#x2F;nvm.sh&quot;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n更新刚配置的环境变量<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">source .bash_profile<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>使用node安装node</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">nvm install stable<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>此时node npm 已经安装完毕，验证一下</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">node -v\nnpm -v <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"安装Hexo\"><a href=\"#安装Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Hexo\"></a>安装Hexo</h2><h3 id=\"npm安装\"><a href=\"#npm安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"npm安装\"></a>npm安装</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">npm install -g hexo-cli<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>如果卡在了fetchMetadata就用开VPN或者换npm的安装源</p>\n<ol>\n<li>换成阿里源</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">npm config set registry https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>验证命令<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">npm config get registry<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>返回<a href=\"https://registry.npm.taobao.org,说明镜像配置成功./\">https://registry.npm.taobao.org，说明镜像配置成功。</a></p></blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>安装cnpm<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">npm install -g cnpm --registry&#x3D;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>接着安装Hexo</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">cnpm install -g hexo-cli<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>成功</p>\n<h3 id=\"初始化Hexo\"><a href=\"#初始化Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化Hexo\"></a>初始化Hexo</h3><p>创建一个文件夹，作为Hexo的根目录（Hexo换成自己建的文件名）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">cd Hexo\nhexo init\nnpm install<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>创建完成，按以下命令启动本地站</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo cl <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> hexo g <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> hexo s<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>启动成功，浏览器输入localhost:4000后回车，即可看到默认的欢迎页面</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装主题\"><a href=\"#安装主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装主题\"></a>安装主题</h3><p>主题官网<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">https://hexo.io/themes/</a>选一个</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>安装主题</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>进入 myblog目录</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">cd Hexo<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>安装主题默认用以下命令（主题文档没有特别说明的话）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">$ git clone 主题github地址 themes&#x2F;主题名<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>修改配置</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>打开根目录Hexo下的_config.yml文件，找到 theme 字段，并将其值更改为刚设置的主题名</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">theme: 主题名<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>修改后保存 然后直接刷新页面就可以看到效果了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"注册github并创建仓库\"><a href=\"#注册github并创建仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注册github并创建仓库\"></a>注册github并创建仓库</h2><h2 id=\"部署到github\"><a href=\"#部署到github\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署到github\"></a>部署到github</h2>","text":"安装 GIT检验是否安装git使用如下命令： $ git --version 然后回车，显示如下git版本号，表示已经安装过git。 git version 2.30.1 (Apple Git-130) 安装git 使用如下命令，先检查是否安装homebrew。$ brew -v...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.8k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Cate","slug":"Cate","count":24,"path":"api/categories/Cate.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Tag","slug":"Tag","count":24,"path":"api/tags/Tag.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-GIT\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装 GIT</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A3%80%E9%AA%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85git\"><span class=\"toc-text\">检验是否安装git</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85git\"><span class=\"toc-text